                                <component>modules/benchmark</component>
                        <due></due>
                    <votes>0</votes>
                        <watches>0</watches>
                                                    <comments>
                    <comment id="12743355" author="koji" created="Fri, 14 Aug 2009 19:40:42 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;The patch introduces a boolean property enwikiQueryMaker.disableSpanQueries. If it is set to true (default is false), EnwikiQueryMaker doesn&apos;t make SpanQueries.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;results (elapsedSec) are:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;table class=&apos;confluenceTable&apos;&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th class=&apos;confluenceTh&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th class=&apos;confluenceTh&apos;&gt;FastVectorHL&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th class=&apos;confluenceTh&apos;&gt;HL&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt;w/o patch&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt;7.70&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt;20.25&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt;w/ patch&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt;7.67&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt;19.07&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
</comment>
                    <comment id="12743535" author="koji" created="Sat, 15 Aug 2009 05:05:45 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Because FastVectorHighlighter&apos;s strength is the performance when processing large docs, this patch includes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;set max.field.length Integer.MAX_VALUE in the alg file&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;introduces a new property &quot;highlighter.maxDocCharsToAnalyze&quot; and set it Integer.MAX_VALUE in the alg file&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
                    <comment id="12743666" author="mikemccand" created="Sat, 15 Aug 2009 10:56:13 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch looks good, thanks Koji.  I&apos;ll commit shortly!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                    <comment id="12743667" author="mikemccand" created="Sat, 15 Aug 2009 11:06:52 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks Koji!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
